<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="un2008c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="un2" href="#un2008">UN2: </a>  <a href="../../FF/unbs/un2all.htm#un2008c"> (VI.D.7) 8(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Paris A large black box found at Louvre, Nap 1st horse, white stuffed horse, branded N on l thigh</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">NAPOLEON&apos;S HORSE.&mdash;Our <mark>Paris</mark> Correspondent telegraphs that <mark>a large box was recently found at the Louvre</mark> Palace bearing in big <mark>black</mark> letters the following inscription:&mdash;&ldquo;To the head of the Imperial Museums in Paris. The Emperor <mark>Napoleon the First&apos;s horse</mark>. From the Natural History Society, Manchester.&rdquo; On opening the box it was found to contain a <mark>white stuffed horse</mark> with small brown spots. <mark>On the left thigh was branded the letter &ldquo;N.&rdquo;</mark> with the Imperial Crown. <small> <a name="TT17jun04" href="/udra/udex.htm#TT17jun04"><cite title="source">The Times</cite></a> (London, 17 June 1904), 6/2</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c16237i" href="../../../F/FF/fnbs/c16all.htm#c16237i">VI.C.16:237(i)</a> </dd> </dd></dl>
